Brand:

{requestData.brand}

Condition:

{requestData.condition}

Model:

{requestData.model}

Year:

{requestData.year}

Pickup Location:

{requestData.pickupLocation}

Delivery Location:

{requestData.deliveryLocation}

Pickup Date:

{requestData.pickupDate}

Delivery Date:

{requestData.deliveryDate}
); }; export default FullRequest;
